title: Puerto Ricans flee to Florida, struggle to find housing
text:
Puerto Ricans flee to Florida, struggle to find housing 2:11pm GMT - 01:46 
About 300,000 Puerto Ricans have fled to Florida in the aftermath of Hurricane Maria, but struggle to find affordable housing in the state which is now cracking at the seams to accommodate them.
